@elementcase is the original innovator; turning up the volume on iPhone case design since 2007.
We repost #elementcase

node.text: The BLACK OPS X3 by @elementcase uses precision CNC machining to deliver an intensely rugged profile that exceeds US MIL-SPEC standards to provide armored protection for your iPhone.

node.text:
The SPECIAL OPS for the iPhone 13 Series is ready for duty! Order the tactically rugged case by @elementcase, and deliver safe cover through advanced engineering principles that deflect and diffuse impact, so your new device is always ready for action.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: The BLACK OPS AirPods Case exceeds military spec MIL-STD-810H, so you can carry your AirPods with confidence shielded by @elementcase.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase. May be an image of phone.

node.text: The SPECIAL OPS delivers the reliable protection you demand from @elementcase. Designed to provide MIL-SPEC drop protection by diffusing impact energy away from your device, it will keep your phone in operational condition even if your tactical descent doesn’t go as planned.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case on September 11, 2021. May be an image of monument, skyscraper and text.
Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: The BLACK OPS X3 delivers solid protection for how you carry your phone, plus the convenience of a removable card magazine, and a retractable kickstand for hands-free viewing.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase. May be an image of saddle-stitched leather.

node.text: The BLACK OPS AirPods Case delivers the protection you need to do it with confidence! Knowing your AirPods are shielded by @elementcase is all you need to know to never hold back.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase.

node.text: Your phone will be safe anywhere because it’s under the protection of SPECIAL OPS by @elementcase; a case that exceeds MIL-SPEC standards with shock deflection armor technology that deflects and absorbs impact to deliver extreme drop protection.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Element Case in San Diego, California with @elementcase, @oakley, and @boker_knives.

node.text: With its removable card magazine, MIL-SPEC protection, and integrated glass breaker, the BLACK OPS X3 by @elementcase adds a tactical profile to how you carry your phone, your cash, and credit cards.

node.text: The right case for the job, the BLACK OPS AirPods Case delivers the protection you’ve come to depend on from @elementcase.

node.text: Make your EDC stand out, and provide the extreme protection your lifestyle demands. The @elementcase collection delivers protection for your @apple AirPods, Apple Watch, and iPhone.
